headline: Prediction: 2 Stocks That Will Be Worth More Than Palantir Technologies 1 Year From Now
summary: Palantir Technologies (NASDAQ: PLTR) has witnessed a tremendous increase in its market value in 2024 thanks to a remarkable surge of 313% in the company's stock price so far this year.  The 20 analysts covering Palantir have a 12-month median price target of $38, which would be a 46% drop from current levels.  If that does indeed happen, its valuation could drop big time in the coming year.
